Title: SANCTUARY
Body: Date: Tue, 10 Dec 1996 22:32:39 GMT Server: NCSA/1.4.2 Content-type: text/html Last-modified: Fri, 24 May 1996 22:46:47 GMT Content-length: 2044 SANCTUARY Art by Ikegami Ryouichi Written by Fumimura Sho SANCTUARY is a  story about two young men working together to change the shape of Tokyo's politics - one by becoming a politician, and the other by becoming a Yakuza.
